\pard\b\f0\fs26 Audit Note\par
\pard\b0\fs22 Bu hujjat lokal repo auditiga asoslangan. Repo ichida topilgan live domenlar: b2b.prohome.uz va sales.prohome.uz. Benchmark sifatida ko'rsatilgan Sales House URL'i foydalanuvchi tomonidan yuborilmaganligi sababli, ushbu versiya to'liq side-by-side benchmark audit emas, balki joriy mahsulotning kritik product, UX, CRO va business auditidir.\par
\par
\pard\b\fs26 1. Executive Summary\par
\pard\b0\fs22 Hozirgi ProHome Sales mahsuloti operatsion chuqurlik bo'yicha kuchli, lekin product polish, orientation va commercial readiness bo'yicha notekis. Tizim ichida foydali modullar bor, ammo foydalanuvchi birinchi kirgan paytda premium, to'liq va ishonchli tizim hissini har doim ham olmaydi.\par
\par
