\pard\tx360\tab - TJM va contract flow kuchli, CRM esa semantik va strukturaviy jihatdan zaifroq.\par
\pard\tx360\tab - Dashboard zamonaviy ko'rinadi, lekin actionability darajasi yetarli emas.\par
\pard\tx360\tab - UI komponentlari yaxshi, lekin product orchestration notekis.\par
\pard\tx360\tab - Production ichida "Tez kunda" kabi unfinished signallar trustni pasaytiradi.\par
